            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_a4Z3" id="i-블록체인-개요">I. 블록체인 개요<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain/#i-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D%EC%B2%B4%EC%9D%B8-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2>
