<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_a4Z3" id="ii-구성">II. 구성<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain/#ii-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2>
